title: GDA’s Syed Muhammad Rashid Shah wins PS- 31 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Grand Democratic Alliance (GDA), Syed Muhammad Rashid Shah has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-31, Kahairpur-6, by securing 58,091 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Muhammad Bachal Shah of Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians (PPPP), who bagged votes 51,769.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 46.85 %.
